{"tid":1082919,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[我佛你] Acer 推智能佛珠 每條經祈福儀式加持","createTime":"2019-03-29T09:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T11:45:30.000Z","uid":44569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c45a9c36c32c80ccf7ebfc71c68e7381c166a897","tid":1082919,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:02:36.000Z","msg":"去年一月， Acer 曾推出智能佛珠 Leap Beads ，為用家記錄誦經次數等數據。如今， Acer 再下一城，與台灣大甲鎮瀾宮合作，於當地即將舉行「大甲媽祖遶境九天八夜進香活動」之際，推出大甲媽祖智能佛珠。除功能與去年推出的大致一樣以外，每條佛珠亦經過大甲鎮瀾宮誦經、過爐及祈福等儀式，希望得到神力加持。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-03-27-10.39-694x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2019-03-27-10.39-694x400.jpg&h=95df5291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據官方網站表示，大甲媽祖智能佛珠分為「清香崖柏」及「金星紫檀限量版」兩款，除了才料有所不同外，「金星紫檀限量版」更同時附有一個佛珠專用無線充電藍牙喇叭，幫助用家誦經修煉。<br />\n而兩款智能佛珠都分別由一粒直徑 2cm 的電子主珠及 13 粒直徑為 1.5cm 的子硃組成。主珠內裝有無線充電晶片，同時附有專用無線充電底座，方便用家充電使用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/%E9%80%81%E7%B6%93%E9%81%8E%E7%88%90%E8%B3%9C%E7%A6%8F-694x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F%25E9%2580%2581%25E7%25B6%2593%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2588%2590%25E8%25B3%259C%25E7%25A6%258F-694x400.jpg&h=046b6015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而透過專用應用程式，用家可以選擇播放適合打坐及念經的音樂。同時設有一系列健康監察功能，包括喝水及睡眠監控、運動及體重管理等。同時照顧用家心靈及身體上的健康需要。大甲媽祖智能佛珠現已於官方網頁及台灣各間旗艦店有售。「清香崖柏」定價為新台幣 3,888 元（約港幣 HK$ 988元）、而「金星紫檀限量版」定價則為新台幣 8,888。（約港幣 HK$ 2260元）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/03/28/acer-leap-beads-new/life-tech/health/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F28%2Facer-leap-beads-new%2Flife-tech%2Fhealth%2F&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HbXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=c1b89e02\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/03/28/acer-leap-beads-new/life-tech/health/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5801d6bd901cac33265137f0cee9abe260ea021e","tid":1082919,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T11:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}